data.description: Here is your chance to own a beautiful slice of St Petersburg Paradise!  NO HOA, NO FLOOD ZONE, and most major systems of the home have been updated!  New sewer lines (2022), New AC (2022), New impact-resistant sliding glass door (2022), Newer roof (2019), Newer impact-resistant windows (2019), AND a brand new above-ground pool with new sand pump (2023)!  You won't have to spend a penny maintaining this home for years!  As an added bonus, you'll appreciate the indoor laundry area, split floorplan, HUGE primary bedroom closet (it's almost like its own room!), enormous fenced-in backyard, and large open kitchen.  Additionally, this lot is home to the streetlight that illuminates the back alleyway so it's safe, private, and secure!  Enjoy the centralized location to both downtown St Pete and our award-winning beaches, as well as the proximity to Clearwater, Tampa, and Bradenton!  You're never too far from the hustle and bustle of restaurants, nightlife, family-friendly activities, or our local airports- what more can anyone ask for?!  Call today to schedule your private showing!
